WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Crossik' is a Workbench game based on the 'sliding-tiles-games'
but with a difference: in the game you have to slide tiles that
contain crosses of various shapes and colours, the goal is simply
to put all pairs of crosses that are of the same type (...and
preferably of the same colour) together.

  When two similar crosses are next to each other, these crosses
are then removed from the game board, but the tiles they were on
remain. Points are given for pairs of crosses that are put
together, but if the crosses are of the same colour, you get more
points... as you may guess, the general idea is to get the highest
possible score...

  Have fun!

